An '''arhythmic resonance scheme''' was a technique that involved running a [[positive flow regulator]] from a power cable into a [[negative flow coupler]]. The resulting explosion was considered quite destructive.

[[Lando Calrissian/Legends|Lando Calrissian]] and [[Chewbacca/Legends|Chewbacca]] used an arhythmic resonance scheme to destroy the [[Mount Tantiss/Legends|Mount Tantiss]] storehouse on [[Wayland/Legends|Wayland]].

